01:01:33.600 --> 01:01:36.620
and move it by a distance.

01:01:36.620 --> 01:01:39.380
Actually, 5 was
probably not good.

01:01:39.380 --> 01:01:40.600
5.14.

01:01:40.600 --> 01:01:43.299
It's not just anything
I can put over here.

01:01:43.299 --> 01:01:44.257
Energy will not change.

01:01:49.127 --> 01:01:51.730
OK?

01:01:51.730 --> 01:01:53.840
AUDIENCE: That must be
different from adding

01:01:53.840 --> 01:02:00.140
to all the ends a
